com.anji.neat

Class AddNeuronMutationOperator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jgapcustomised.MutationOperator
      • com.anji.neat.MutationOperatorMultiple
        • com.anji.neat.AddNeuronMutationOperator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Configurable

    public class AddNeuronMutationOperator
extends MutationOperatorMultiple
implements Configurable
    Implements NEAT add node mutation inspired by Evolving Neural Networks through Augmenting Topologies . Note that if the classic mutation scheme is enabled (see NeatConfiguration.TOPOLOGY_MUTATION_CLASSIC_KEY) then SingleTopologicalMutationOperator calls addNeuronAtConnection(NeatConfiguration, Map, ConnectionAllele, Set, Set) directly, otherwise the number of mutations is determined by MutationOperatorMultiple.numMutations(Random, int).
    Author:
    Philip Tucker, Oliver Coleman

Note that if the classic mutation scheme is enabled (see NeatConfiguration.TOPOLOGY_MUTATION_CLASSIC_KEY) then this method is not used and instead SingleTopologicalMutationOperator calls addNeuronAtConnection(NeatConfiguration, Map, ConnectionAllele, Set, Set) directly.
